        <h1>Tax Filing Deadline 2026: All Key Dates Explained</h1>
        <p class="qa-meta">Updated May 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Covers tax year 2025 returns filed in 2026</p>
        <p>The federal income tax filing deadline for tax year 2025 returns is April 15, 2026. If you filed an extension, your deadline is October 15, 2026. Missing either deadline without paying what you owe triggers IRS penalties and interest.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-answer">
        <div class="qa-label">Quick Answer: 2026 Tax Deadlines</div>
        <h2>Key dates for your 2025 tax return</h2>
        <div class="deadline-grid">
